name: #bouncingFRAME17
description:
The animated version of my frame for a collaboration with 24 artists on HEN initiated by @jeremy_pires.

#bouncingOBJKT24 is a small testimony of the amazing #nftcommunity that #HEN has built and made possible. A Bouncing OBJKT made of 24 frames from 24 HEN artists all gathered in 1 loop. Thanks to all those kind and talented people, we are the #24for24.
